                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5661" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0281</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8592 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">善于“走心”，勇于“走新”： 北京管道陕西处文化建设如何走实走远</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Diligently and Innovatively: How the Organization Culture Construction of Beijing Pipeline Company, Shaanxi Department Walk Steady to Reach the Distance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蒋晓荣，秦婧怡，宁小强，刘莉</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国家管网集团北京管道有限公司陕西输气管理处</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">党群部门/思想政治工作部门/企业文化部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">22 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京管道陕西处；党建；组织文化；组织文化建设；2021百优案例；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Shaanxi Department of Beijing Pipeline; Party building; Organizational Culture; Organizational Culture Construction </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国有企业在经营管理中，必须坚持和加强党的全面领导，确保各项改革举措的有效实施，把党建工作的制度优势转化为管理优势，以推动国有企业的不断发展。本案例以“文化探索→文化推进→文化引领→文化熏陶→文化影响”的逻辑主线展开描述，北京管道陕西处管理层大胆探索，基于总公司组织文化，结合企业的实际情况，文化建设融入党建元素，确立了陕西处组织文化的核心价值观，扎实推进“四定六增”工作法，以党建促进制度落实，明确规范，其中，管理层党员身体力行、率先垂范，支部以党建为抓手，开展系列活动，普通党员积极行动，党建加强与文化建设齐头并进。然后，陕西处借助榜样宣传及“管道&#183;家庭&#183;爱”系列活动使全体员工感受文化，进一步推动组织文化落地，最终，陕西处以其独具特色的组织文化，积极影响利益相关者。进而，影响企业社会绩效和经济绩效，文化积极效果显现。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the operation and management, state-owned enterprises must adhere and strengthen the overall leadership of the Party to ensure the effective implementation of various reform measures and transform the institutional advantages of Party building into management advantages. So as to promote the continuous development of state-owned enterprises. This case describes the logic of &quot;culture promoting → culture lead → culture influence&quot;, Beijing pipeline Shaanxi management bold exploration, based on corporation organization culture and combined with the actual situation of the enterprise, then established the core values of Shaanxi organization culture and promoted the &quot;four set six increase&quot; working method and system implementation, clear specification, among them, management party members branch to party construction, series of activities, ordinary party construction to strengthen hand in hand with cultural construction. Then, Shaanxi Department worked with the help of example publicity and a series of activities of &quot;Pipeline &#183; Family &#183; Love&quot; to make all employees feel the culture and further promote the implementation of organizational culture. Finally, Shaanxi Department used its unique organizational culture to actively affect the stakeholders.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《人力资源管理》、《管理学原理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织文化</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
